<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="mn">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>UTDX Wiki | Universal Tower Defense X</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px; background: #0f0f23; color: #ddd; }
        header { background: linear-gradient(#1a1a3d, #0a0a1f); padding: 40px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 6px solid #ffcc00; }
        h1, h2, h3 { color: #ffcc00; }
        nav { background: #1a1a3d; padding: 15px; text-align: center; }
        nav a { color: #ffcc00; margin: 15px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
        .content { max-width: 1200px; margin: auto; }
        .section { background: #1a1a3d; padding: 25px; margin: 25px 0; border-radius: 12px; }
        .search-bar { width: 100%; padding: 15px; font-size: 18px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; border: none; }
        .unit-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
        .unit-card { background: #2a2a4d; border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; }
        .unit-card:hover { transform: scale(1.08); box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ffcc00; }
        .unit-card img { width: 100%; max-height: 220px; object-fit: contain; border: 3px solid #ffcc00; border-radius: 8px; }
        .modal { display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9); z-index: 1000; }
        .modal-content { background: #1a1a3d; margin: 10% auto; padding: 20px; width: 80%; max-width: 600px; border-radius: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>🌌 UTDX Wiki (JavaScript-тай)</h1>
        <p>Update 3.0 - Хайлт хийж үзээрэй!</p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="#units">Units</a>
        <a href="#traits-relics">Trait & Relic</a>
        <a href="#guides">Guides</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="content">
        <input type="text" id="searchInput" class="search-bar" placeholder="Unit нэрээр хай... (Luffy, Jinoo гэх мэт)" onkeyup="filterUnits()">

        <div id="units" class="section">
            <h2>Meta Units (Дарвал дэлгэрэнгүй)</h2>
            <div class="unit-grid" id="unitGrid">
                <!-- JavaScript-ээр нэмэгдэнэ -->
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="traits-relics" class="section">
            <h2>Trait & Relic</h2>
            <p>Trait = Unit-ын супер хүч. Ruler trait олох гэж их roll хийнэ.</p>
            <p>Relic = Хувцас. Warlord set хамгийн сайн.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="guides" class="section">
            <h2>Guides</h2>
            <p>Meta team бариарай. Ruler trait + Warlord relic = хамгийн хүч